msgid ""
"Kontrast is a color contrast checker and tells you if your color "
"combinations are distinct enough to be readable and accessible."
msgstr ""
"Kontrast es un verificator de contrasto e te dice si tu combinationes de "
"color es assatis distincte per esser legibile e accessibile."

